<?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8"?><song><title>ạḥfẓ ḥyạty lykwn</title>
<lyrics>[V1]
 1- ạiḥ̊faẓ̊ ḥayātī līakūn̊
 tak̊rīsuhā yā rabũ lak̊
 wāḥ̊faẓ̊nī daẘmaⁿạ sẖākiraⁿạ
 ṭūla ạlzãmāni ʿamalak̊

[V2]
 2- wāḥ̊faẓ̊ yadī muḥarĩkaⁿạ
 lahā biḥubĩka ạl̊ʿaẓīm̊
 wāḥ̊faẓ̊ kẖuṭay̱ rij̊layã fī
 sulūki ṭur̊qika ạl̊qawīm̊

[V3]
 3- ṣaẘtī ạḥ̊faẓan̊ muranĩmạ
 lisayĩdī ṭūla ạl̊maday̱
 wasẖafatāya ạḥ̊faẓ̊humā
 lilnũṭ̊qi bibusẖ̊ray̱ ạl̊fiday̱

[V4]
 4- ại̹rādatī ạḥ̊faẓ̊ fah̊ya lak̊
 laẙsa murādī ạlậna lī
 qal̊bī ạḥ̊faẓan̊ fayum̊talak̊
 biḥubĩ sẖakẖ̊ṣika ạl̊ʿalī̃̊

[V5]
 5- ḥubĩy ạḥ̊faẓan̊hu, dẖākẖiraⁿạ
 ại̹yãạhu kāl̊kan̊zi ạltẖãmīn̊
 wakun̊ linaf̊sī ḥāfiẓaⁿạ
 ại̹nĩy ḍaʿīfuⁿ yā muʿīn̊</lyrics>
<copyright>Public Domain</copyright>
<author>Mozart, Wolfgang Amadeus (1756-1791), Havergal, Frances Ridley (1836-1879), Frances Ridley Havergal</author>
</song>